Comment: Good one

Goal
* Please delete everything below point 4 and add the following instead:

Exception: When [[s]] is {{A}} or {{a}} or {{B}} or {{b}}, you must output {{ERROR}} as it is impossible to distinguish between a filled square and a hollow square when [[length]] is 1 or 2.

Output
* Please change "[ Hollow or filled ]" to "or {{ERROR}}".

Cases
* Please swap the cases so that each pair of test and validator is similar, e.g.

Test 1 and Validator 1: small hollow squares
Test 2 and Validator 2: small filled squares
Test 3 and Validator 3: medium hollow squares
Test 4 and Validator 4: medium filled squares
Test 5 and Validator 5: large hollow squares
Test 6 and Validator 6: large filled squares
Test 7: A
Validator 7: B
Test 8: b
Validator 8: a

Thanks.

Wow, you do really take that much time to modify someone's clash. Great job and thank you so much for
that!

Alright one thing, how do I overcome the 
error - "You do not have the last contribution version" 
?

Thank you for your compliments!

For the error, you'll have to refresh your browser to make sure it's loaded the latest version of the contribution.
